reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My teeth feel the clean, like after the dentist clean.
reviews.reviewText: Really great bang for buck! Paid half of what my boyfriend’s electric toothbrush was and he's so jealous. Has so many cleaning settings and comes with 5 extra toothbrush heads! Overall feels high end and not bulky what so ever!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good Toothbrush and does the job and great price
reviews.reviewText: I bought this by mistake. Thought I had ordered an Oral B - it must have been right together with it when I was looking. However, it came with 10 brushes, a case, everything you would need. I have periodontal disease, so I have lots of plaque buildup. This toothbrush has 5 stages you can go through while brushing. I use the top 4 every time I brush. The gums on one of my teeth have receeded so that I could see the root and it looked black. It now just looks gray - after several months. The first time I went for cleaning they told me I had very little plaque build-up compared to what it had been in the past. So I would say this is a very, good sonic toothbrush and the price was very, very good.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars High quality, great service
reviews.reviewText: I immediately liked the MySmile toothbrush and all of its features. 6 months after I bought it, it wouldn't recharge. The company immediately agreed to replace it. In the interim I bought the highly rated Oral B Pro 1000. It didn't hold a candle to the MySmile, which is gentler on the gums and does a great job of cleaning (especially if you use the timer). I would definitely buy it again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The battery life is something to talk about. It lasted for more than sixty day and counting. Excellent for travel without have to take charger along

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great on the go
reviews.reviewText: Works great and the fact it comes with a case is awesome. The case makes it so much easier to brush at work. Mouth has never felt better. Does great on my 4 front venirs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 3, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I had a difficult time the first week trying to get use to this toothbrush, especially the louder sound and different shaped brush head compared with my old electric brush. Nonetheless, I did not give up and just kept making adjustments to my brushing technique, especially since I needed the sensitive setting. Now I love my brush, especially the time notifications and different available settings to meet my needs. My teeth feel great after brushing. The price was excellent including a nice storage case that I will use when traveling, taking up much less space than my old one. Glad I had the patience to keep on trying to get use to this good brush.
